# Place Lottie JSON files here. Suggested filenames used by the app:
#   - report_success.json   (lantern light glow / candle flame minimalist)
#   - empty_notifications.json (calm candle loop)
#   - connection_lost.json   (disconnected dots minimal)
#   - splash_particles.json  (subtle gold particles)
#   - person_found.json      (warm glow burst / peaceful sparkle)
# Download from https://lottiefiles.com using the search terms above.
# Keep each file under 80 KB; prefer monochrome (gold/navy) or color-tinted via colorFilter.
